“About me” ante usually **self-introduction**. Meeru personal profile, resume, GitHub, interview, or bio kosam adugutunnara ani anukuntunna.

Meeru Git / tech context lo untunnaru kabatti, nenu **simple professional “About Me” template** istunna 👇

