# 👤 About Me (Sample)

Hi, I am a passionate software learner interested in **software development and Git/GitHub workflows**.
I enjoy learning new technologies and building projects to improve my skills.

I have experience working with **Git version control**, branches, commits, and basic project management in development environments. I am continuously improving my knowledge in coding and real-time project handling.

My goal is to become a skilled developer and work on real-world applications that solve practical problems.

---

# 🔥 Simple version (for resume / GitHub bio)

I am a software enthusiast with interest in development and version control systems like Git. I like learning new technologies and building projects.

